'''亨利·弗萊徹·漢斯'''（Henry Fletcher Hance，{{bd|1827年|8月4日|1886年|5月22日}}）英國外交官，他用業餘時間在中國和香港研究植物。漢斯生於倫敦，1845年到香港任職公務員，後來歷任英國駐黃埔副領事、駐廣州署理領事、駐廈門署理領事，1886年在廈門去世。<ref>Dictionary of Hong Kong Biography, p173</ref><ref>香港植物標本室-130週年，漁農自然護理署，p10-12</ref>

[[乔治·边沁|乔治·边沁]]1861年的《{{link-es|香港植物誌|Flora Hongkongensis}}》收錄其植物研究<ref>{{cite web | url=http://kiki.huh.harvard.edu/databases/botanist_search.php?botanistid=45417 | title=Hance, Henry Fletcher | publisher=Harvard University Herbaria & Libraries | accessdate=2016-04-18 | archive-date=2016-04-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428074036/http://kiki.huh.harvard.edu/databases/botanist_search.php?botanistid=45417 | dead-url=no }}[http://kiki.huh.harvard.edu/databases/botanist_search.php?botanistid=57667] {{Wayback|url=http://kiki.huh.harvard.edu/databases/botanist_search.php?botanistid=57667 |date=20160428035510 }}</ref>。1875年發表關於[[小花鸢尾|小花鸢尾]]（Iris speculatrix）文獻<ref>{{cite web |title=Thema: Die Planzengattung Iris ...  (Gelesen 5316 mal) |url=http://www.orchideenkultur.net/index.php?topic=28569.30 |publisher=orchideenkultur.net |accessdate=13 January 2015 |archive-date=2016-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402115312/http://www.orchideenkultur.net/index.php?topic=28569.30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Journal of Botany British and Foreign |url=http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/8955130#page/220/mode/1up |publisher=biodiversitylibrary.org |accessdate=15 January 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307103758/http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/8955130#page/220/mode/1up |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[生物分类学|生物分类学]]有諸多貢獻<ref>[http://www.ipni.org/ipni/advPlantNameSearch.do?find_family=&find_genus=&find_species=&find_infrafamily=&find_infragenus=&find_infraspecies=&find_authorAbbrev=Hance&find_includePublicationAuthors=on&find_includePublicationAuthors=off&find_includeBasionymAuthors=on&find_includeBasionymAuthors=off&find_publicationTitle=&find_isAPNIRecord=on&find_isAPNIRecord=false&find_isGCIRecord=on&find_isGCIRecord=false&find_isIKRecord=on&find_isIKRecord=false&find_rankToReturn=all&output_format=normal&find_sortByFamily=on&find_sortByFamily=off&query_type=by_query&back_page=plantsearch IPNI] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ipni.org/ipni/advPlantNameSearch.do?find_family=&find_genus=&find_species=&find_infrafamily=&find_infragenus=&find_infraspecies=&find_authorAbbrev=Hance&find_includePublicationAuthors=on&find_includePublicationAuthors=off&find_includeBasionymAuthors=on&find_includeBasionymAuthors=off&find_publicationTitle=&find_isAPNIRecord=on&find_isAPNIRecord=false&find_isGCIRecord=on&find_isGCIRecord=false&find_isIKRecord=on&find_isIKRecord=false&find_rankToReturn=all&output_format=normal&find_sortByFamily=on&find_sortByFamily=off&query_type=by_query&back_page=plantsearch |date=20180114082433 }} List of plants described and co-described by Hance.</ref>，1857年{{link-de|貝特霍爾德卡爾·基曼|Berthold Carl Seemann}}將[[大戟科|大戟科]]某一屬植物命名為{{tsl|en|Hancea|Hancea屬}}（Hancea）<ref>[http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/33068284#page/68/mode/1up BHL] {{Wayback|url=http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/33068284#page/68/mode/1up |date=20190928230519 }} Taxonomic literature : a selective guide to botanical publications</ref>。

